## Memory & Knowledge

This workspace uses a layered memory system. Optionally, it integrates with **cognee** for semantic search across the corpus.

| Layer | Location | Populated by |
|-------|----------|--------------|
| Personal curated | `<workspace>/.claude/memory/{MEMORY,lessons-learned}.md` | `/bye` |
| Per-project knowledge | `<workspace>/projects/<slug>/.claude/memory/` | `/bye`, committed for repos |
| Identity | `<workspace>/me/{identity,brag-log,growth,team}.md` | `/setup-workspace`, `/bye` |

## Layout

```
{{workspace_path}}/
├── CLAUDE.md                       # this file
├── .claude/
│   ├── skills/  agents/  docs/     # deployed by /setup-workspace
│   ├── memory/                     # workspace MEMORY/lessons
│   ├── settings.json
│   └── projects-index.json         # project registry
├── workstreams/                    # random tasks (gitignored)
├── sessions/active/                # advisory markers (gitignored)
├── collected/                      # skill data (gitignored)
├── artifacts/                      # skill outputs (gitignored)
├── contributions/                  # staged contributions (gitignored)
├── me/                             # identity, brag log, growth
├── source/                         # boilerplate source repos
└── projects/                       # registered projects (gitignored)
```

